    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tri-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピースの沖縄ライブ当日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースの野外ライブをやります！\nすぐそこのビーチです！　よかったら観に来て下さい！",
      "startTime": 5.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4666.666666666666,
          "startTime": 7.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2033.3333333333337,
          "startTime": 4.466666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、こんな所で何してはるん？",
      "startTime": 9.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さん？　そっちこそここで何をしてるんだ？",
      "startTime": 13.033333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "うちはライブ前のサニピを激励しよ思て\n楽屋でみんなに挨拶してきた所や",
      "startTime": 21.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "そこで、{user}さんが\n会場の外にいるって聞いて様子を見に来たんよ",
      "startTime": 26.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか……\nでもどうして衣装を着てるんだ……？",
      "startTime": 32.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちほどの有名人になると飛び入りで\nステージに出てほしいって言われるかもしらんやろ？",
      "startTime": 39.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "せやから楽屋で自前のステージ衣装に着替えてん",
      "startTime": 42.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "どうやろ？　セクシーやろ～",
      "startTime": 46.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "有名人だって自覚はあるんだし\n頼むから……もう少し控えめな格好にしてくれよ",
      "startTime": 52.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは真面目やな～",
      "startTime": 57.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "それで、結局{user}さんは\nここで何してはるんですか？",
      "startTime": 63.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "イベントのスタッフと一緒にビラ配りをしてるんだ",
      "startTime": 66.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ビラ配り？\nそれってマネージャーさんのお仕事なん？",
      "startTime": 71.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、誰の仕事って訳でもないけど\n一人でも多くの人にサニピのライブを観てほしくてね",
      "startTime": 77.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そのために出来ることなら何でもやるさ",
      "startTime": 81.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "ふうん……\nほなうちも手伝うわ、そのビラを配ればええんやろ",
      "startTime": 87.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、イベントと無関係の鈴村さんに\nこんなことをさせる訳には……",
      "startTime": 94.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "無関係やなんてつれないこと言わんといて\nうちらは仲間やろ",
      "startTime": 100.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "うちがやりたいんやから細かいことは言いっこなしや",
      "startTime": 102.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "でもその格好はさすがに目立つだろ",
      "startTime": 106.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "宣伝するんやったら目立った方がええんちゃうの？",
      "startTime": 110.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、トリエルが水着同然の格好で\n客引きしてたら大騒ぎになるから",
      "startTime": 116.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "その時は{user}さんがうちを\n守ってくれるんやろ？",
      "startTime": 121.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "うちがお姫様であんたが白馬の騎士や\n頼りにしてるで～",
      "startTime": 127.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "ほな、張り切ってビラ配りしよか～！",
      "startTime": 129.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "やれやれ……鈴村さんには敵わないな……",
      "startTime": 132.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐイベント開始の時刻やな。会場は満員御礼で\n頑張ってビラを配った甲斐がありましたわ",
      "startTime": 144.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "俺はビラを配ってる間、鈴村さんの正体がばれないか\nずっとヒヤヒヤしてたけどな",
      "startTime": 152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "ヒヤヒヤと言うか、気付いてる人もおったで\n何度か握手を求められましたわ",
      "startTime": 158.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "そういう人には小声で『うちのことは秘密やで』って\nこっそりお願いしたから黙っててくれたみたいやな",
      "startTime": 165.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_02_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "それでなんとかなるんだから\n鈴村さんの対人スキルの高さには感心するよ",
